HBnB Project – Technical Documentation
1. Introduction
Purpose and Scope

This document provides the technical documentation for the HBnB Evolution application. It describes the architecture, system design, core entities, and API interaction flows of the system. The purpose of this document is to provide developers and maintainers with a clear understanding of how the application is structured and how its components interact.

Project Overview

HBnB Evolution is a simplified property rental platform inspired by Airbnb. The application allows users to:

Register and manage accounts

Create and manage property listings (places)

Leave reviews for places

Associate amenities with places

The system follows a layered architecture and applies object-oriented programming principles to ensure modularity, maintainability, and scalability.

